(31442, 10390, 0, 1, '起錨', '香港如何起錨', '2010-10-01 00:00:00', 2000, 0, 2, 10, '你有你的一套哲學\r\n讓我們瞎子般去摸索\r\n你賣廣告 \r\n我當你發嗡瘋亂作 \r\n\r\n你叫我信你信你信你地\r\n但你只懂得賴皮\r\n你叫「李至奇」\r\n我信你老母都好過信你 \r\n\r\n你說被強姦不要反抗\r\n前路要靠商家去開創\r\n你話我激進 \r\n但我有野想講\r\n \r\n我地o既意見你沒有接受\r\n你地o既對話又無狗厘頭\r\n草根o既訴求\r\n你聽不到不等於沒有\r\n \r\n香港賊船要起錨\r\n你無錢無份向前行\r\n香港賊船要起錨\r\n阿公帶路我地要跟住行\r\n\r\n你話你地你地幾巴閉\r\n最低工資點樣計\r\n你有乜所謂  \r\n我慘過盂蘭節去輪米\r\n \r\n你叫我信你信你信你地\r\n但你只懂得賴皮\r\n你叫「李至奇」\r\n我信你老母都好過信你\r\n \r\n香港賊船要起錨\r\n你無錢無份向前行\r\n香港賊船要起錨\r\n阿公帶路要跟住行\r\n\r\n我地支持「李至奇」\r\n我地支持「李至奇」\r\n我地支持「李至奇」\r\n我地支持「李至奇」\r\n \r\n起錨 起錨 起錨 起錨\r\n \r\n話比佢地聽\r\n我地係多數  \r\n佢地係少數\r\n話比佢地聽  \r\n我多謝你咁大聲\r\n\r\nYou have your own philosophy\r\nLeave us fumble like the blind\r\nYou are advertising\r\nBut to me you are speaking nonsense\r\n\r\nYou tell me to trust you, trust you and trust you\r\nBut you are never sincere\r\nYour name is Mr. Marvellous Lee \r\nI''d rather trust your mom than you\r\n\r\nYou say do not react against you\r\nLet the businessmen create the future\r\nYou say I was radical \r\nBut then I also have a say\r\n \r\nYou do not accept our opinions\r\nAnd your feedbacks are even more ridiculous\r\nThe requets from the grassroot\r\nYou do not hear them do not mean they do not exist\r\n \r\nAct Now. Hong Kong Private Ship\r\nYou cannot move forward if you have no money\r\nAct Now. Hong Kong Private Ship\r\nWe have to follow wherever grandpa leads us\r\n \r\nYou say how smart you are\r\nAll different means to calculate the minimum wages\r\nDoes that really matter to you?\r\nHow pitiful I am begging you \r\n \r\nYou say to trust you, you and you\r\nBut you are never sincere\r\nYour name is Mr. Wonderful Lee. \r\nI''d rather believe your mom than you \r\n \r\nAct Now. Hong Kong Private Ship\r\nYou cannot move forward if you have no money\r\nAct Now. Hong Kong Private Ship\r\nWe have to follow wherever grandpa leads us \r\n\r\nWe support Mr. Marvellous Lee\r\nWe support Mr. Wonderful Lee\r\nWe support Mr. Marvellous Lee\r\nWe support Mr. Won